<template><div><h2 id="_7-5-7-2022-09-25" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-5-7-2022-09-25" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/compare/7.5.6...7.5.7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">7.5.7<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> (2022-09-25)</h2>
