</ul>
<h1 id="_7-2-0-2021-07-05" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_7-2-0-2021-07-05" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/compare/7.1.0...7.2.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">7.2.0<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> (2021-07-05)</h1>
