<li><strong>Subscription:</strong> use <code v-pre>instanceof</code> to avoid megamorphic LoadIC (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/issues/4499" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#4499<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>) (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/commit/065b4e3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">065b4e3<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
