<li><strong>Observable.prototype.pipe:</strong> TS typings now more correct for &gt;8 parameters (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/issues/3789" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#3789<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>) (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/commit/ad010ea" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ad010ea<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
<li><strong>subscribe:</strong> ignore syncError when deprecated (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/issues/3749" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#3749<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>) (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/commit/f94560c" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">f94560c<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
<li><strong>Symbol.observable:</strong> make observable declaration readonly (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/issues/3697" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#3697<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>) (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/issues/3773" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#3773<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>) (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/commit/e1c203f" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">e1c203f<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
<li><strong>TypeScript:</strong> resolved typings issue for TS 3.0 (<a href="https://github.com/reactivex/rxjs/commit/bf2cdeb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">bf2cdeb<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
