<li><strong>typings:</strong> correct compilation warnings from missing types in tests (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/3aad6bc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3aad6bc<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
<li><strong>typings:</strong> relax debounce selector type (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/c419ab4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">c419ab4<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>), closes <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/issues/3164" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#3164<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
