<li><strong>skipLast:</strong> add skipLast operator (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/issues/2316" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#2316<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>) (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/4ffbbe5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">4ffbbe5<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>), closes <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/issues/1404" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#1404<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
