<h1 id="_5-2-0-2017-02-21" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_5-2-0-2017-02-21" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/compare/5.1.1...v5.2.0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5.2.0<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> (2017-02-21)</h1>
