<p><a name="5.0.0-beta.6"></a></p>
<h1 id="_5-0-0-beta-6-2016-04-12" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#_5-0-0-beta-6-2016-04-12" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/compare/5.0.0-beta.5...v5.0.0-beta.6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">5.0.0-beta.6<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> (2016-04-12)</h1>
<h3 id="bug-fixes-102" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#bug-fixes-102" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Bug Fixes</h3>
<ul>
