<li><strong>bufferToggle:</strong> accepts promise as openings (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/3d22c7a" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">3d22c7a<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
<li><strong>bufferToggle:</strong> handle closingSelector completes immediately (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/02239fb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">02239fb<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
<li><strong>typings:</strong> explicitly export typings for arguments to functions that destructure configuration objects (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/ef305af" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ef305af<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
