<li><strong>exhaustMap:</strong> remove innersubscription when it completes (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/7ca0859" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">7ca0859<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>)</li>
