<h3 id="breaking-changes-30" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#breaking-changes-30" aria-hidden="true">#</a> BREAKING CHANGES</h3>
<ul>
<li>Subject: Subject.create arguments have been swapped to match Rx 4 signature. <code v-pre>Subject.create(observable, observer)</code> is now <code v-pre>Subject.create(observer, observable)</code></li>
<li>Observable patching: Patch files for static observable methods such as <code v-pre>of</code> and <code v-pre>from</code> can now be found in <code v-pre>rxjs/add/observable/of</code>, <code v-pre>rxjs/add/observable/from</code>, etc.</li>
<li>Observable modules: Observable modules for subclassed Observables like <code v-pre>PromiseObservable</code>, <code v-pre>ArrayObservable</code> are now in appropriately named files like <code v-pre>rxjs/observable/PromiseObservable</code> and <code v-pre>rxjs/observable/ArrayObservable</code>
as opposed to <code v-pre>rxjs/observable/fromPromise</code> and <code v-pre>rxjs/observable/fromArray</code>, since they're not patching, they simply house the Observable implementations.</li>
</ul>
