<li><strong>zip:</strong> zip now supports never-ending iterables (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/a5684ba" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">a5684ba<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>), closes <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/issues/397" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#397<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
