<li><strong>VirtualTimeScheduler:</strong> add VirtualTimeScheduler (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/96f9386" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">96f9386<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>), closes <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/issues/269" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#269<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
<li><strong>operator:</strong> add sample and sampleTime (<a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/commit/9e62789" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">9e62789<ExternalLinkIcon/></a>), closes <a href="https://github.com/ReactiveX/RxJS/issues/178" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">#178<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
</ul>
